videos.headline: RJ Davis scores 5 quick points to retake lead
videos.description: After Elon pulled ahead against North Carolina, R.J. Davis scores 5 quick points to help stem the tide for the Tar Heels.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (RJ Davis scores 5 quick points to retake lead) 2024/11/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cadeau and Davis get Tar Heels going with back-to-back 3s
videos.description: The North Carolina Tar Heels first baskets of the season come from Elliot Cadeau and RJ Davis three-pointers.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Cadeau and Davis get Tar Heels going with back-to-back 3s) 2024/11/4 ESHEET

videos.headline: Drake Powell cashes a 3
videos.description: Drake Powell gets the three-pointer to go for the Tar Heels.

videos.headline: Seth Trimble skies for an alley-oop
videos.description: Drake Powell feeds Seth Trimble in transition for the alley-oop dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Seth Trimble skies for an alley-oop) 2024/11/4 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ian Jackson gets his first bucket as a Tar Heel
videos.description: Ian Jackson catches Elliot Cadeau's lob in transition for a Tar Heel bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Ian Jackson gets his first bucket as a Tar Heel) 2024/11/4 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jalen Washington lets out a yell after slamming one home
videos.description: Elliot Cadeau drives and finds Jalen Washington for the close-range flush.
